graph TD
    A[User Request] --> B{Does User ID Exist?}
    
    subgraph Persistent State
    B -->|Yes| C[Read from Store]
    B -->|No| D[Create New Namespace]
    C --> E[Extract User Preferences]
    D --> F[Write Default Preferences to Store]
    
    E --> G[Generate Response with Context]
    F --> G
    end
    
    subgraph Multi-Turn Memory
    G --> H[Update Thread Checkpoint]
    H -->|User Returns Later| A
    end
    
    G --> I[Final Response]
